works.description: Designer Nika Zupanc is known for her aesthetic taste. We have earlier told you about her Konstantin Beta ride-on toy designed for 20LTD and her “Gone with the wind” furniture collection at Milan fair, 2010. The latest from this Slovenian designer is a steampunk furniture collection called “Self Discipline” at the Salone Milan 2011. The collection includes a chandelier, desk, chair and cabinets controlled with brass levers in traditional style. The retro looks are combined with hidden storage that is controlled with the lever mechanism.
